OpenILS-QueryParser version 0.01
================================

SYNOPSIS

The OpenILS::QueryParser module is used by the Evergreen open source
integrated library system and the Koha open source integrated library
system for parsing users' queries. The parser is interfaced to the
underlying search engines with implementation-specific drivers

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  JSON

